            <p>
              We may use third-party advertising companies, including Google AdSense, to display advertisements on our website. These services help us keep the calculator free for all users.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-5 my-4">
              <p class="text-blue-800 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">Google AdSense</p>
              <div class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
                <p>Google AdSense may use cookies, including the DoubleClick cookie, to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website and other sites on the Internet.</p>
