                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 pt-2">Third-Party Vendors</h3>
            <p>
              Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits. These ad networks use technology to deliver advertisements directly to your browser and may automatically receive your IP address in the process.
