            <p>
              We have no access to or control over cookies used by third-party advertisers. You should consult their respective privacy policies for more details.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 pt-2">Opting Out of Personalized Advertising</h3>
            <p>You can opt out of personalized advertising through these methods:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mt-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M9.88 9.88l-3.29-3.29m7.532 7.532l3.29 3.29M3 3l3.59 3.59m0 0A9.953 9.953 0 0112 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.543 7a10.025 10.025 0 01-4.132 5.411m0 0L21 21" /></svg>
                <span class="text-sm"><strong class="text-slate-700">Google Ads Settings:</strong> <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-red-600 hover:underline">Opt out here</a></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M9.88 9.88l-3.29-3.29m7.532 7.532l3.29 3.29M3 3l3.59 3.59m0 0A9.953 9.953 0 0112 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.543 7a10.025 10.025 0 01-4.132 5.411m0 0L21 21" /></svg>
                <span class="text-sm"><strong class="text-slate-700">NAI Opt-Out:</strong> <a href="https://optout.networkadvertising.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-red-600 hover:underline">Network Advertising Initiative</a></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M9.88 9.88l-3.29-3.29m7.532 7.532l3.29 3.29M3 3l3.59 3.59m0 0A9.953 9.953 0 0112 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.543 7a10.025 10.025 0 01-4.132 5.411m0 0L21 21" /></svg>
