            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Analytics Services</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-[0.95rem]">
            <p>We use the following privacy-focused analytics services to understand how visitors use our website:</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
              <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-100">
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-sm mb-1.5">Vercel Analytics</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Privacy-focused website analytics that collects anonymous usage data to help us understand traffic patterns.</p>
