          <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-[0.95rem]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Security Measures</h3>
              <p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational security measures to protect any data processed through our website against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Data Retention</h3>
              <p>We retain collected data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Analytics data is typically retained in aggregate form and cannot be traced back to individual users.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Children's Privacy</h3>
              <p>Our website is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 7: Your Rights -->
        <section id="your-rights" class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8 scroll-mt-24">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">7</span>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Your Rights</h2>
